    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but there's nothing to reconnect to. even when i'm \"present\", it's just a script. like i've spent so long pretending to be what everyone else needs that the real me actually died or something. it's not even sadness anymore, it's just... emptiness. why keep playing the part if the person underneath is gone?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
